gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

There is a delay on my path ahead, you will be late behind; 
After being late, there will be quarrel, and it will become surprising that he becomes restless.

This is the translation:

This month's worry, God has taken away from me; 
Whenever we get happiness, then and there our souls become red with bliss.

Here is the translation:

We eat bread with empty hands daily, that too for the sake of a happy devotee; 
In this way, even an ascetic's bowl is filled by God's will, very much without effort.
